WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.920
Good morning, family. I'm excited

00:00:03.179 --> 00:00:07.980
to be able to come on today and

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:10.379
introduce to you

00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:14.160
my wife, Diana. We've been married for

00:00:10.380 --> 00:00:15.960
22 years. I'm really excited;

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:18.480
she's been the person in the

00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:20.460
background. She's the one that

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:22.619
reads all the emails and

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:24.539
comments to me, and she's helping respond.

00:00:22.619 --> 00:00:26.519
She's been a real big part of this,

00:00:24.539 --> 00:00:28.619
and we just want to say thank you

00:00:26.519 --> 00:00:30.659
for all the financial blessings

00:00:28.619 --> 00:00:33.059
you've given our family and for the support—the

00:00:30.660 --> 00:00:35.460
likes and shares.

00:00:33.059 --> 00:00:37.680
YouTube's really tried to

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:39.780
suppress my videos lately. We can

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:41.820
see on our little chart what they've

00:00:39.780 --> 00:00:44.040
done, and my videos are just being

00:00:41.820 --> 00:00:46.620
seen by you all. So, I just wanted to

00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:48.719
say thank you for sharing my stuff and for helping

00:00:46.620 --> 00:00:51.419
support getting the gospel out

00:00:48.719 --> 00:00:54.239
there, telling people that Jesus

00:00:51.420 --> 00:00:56.879
Christ loves them. We're just so

00:00:54.239 --> 00:00:59.578
honored and thankful for all that you've

00:00:56.879 --> 00:01:01.500
done for us. Diana, do

00:00:59.579 --> 00:01:02.879
you have anything you want to say? "No, I

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:05.159
just wanted to say thank you for all

00:01:02.879 --> 00:01:06.600
your support. We enjoy reading your

00:01:05.159 --> 00:01:08.640
comments.

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:10.199
We always read them, and if we don't

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:12.180
respond, just know that we're always

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:13.979
praying over you. Everything that we

00:01:12.180 --> 00:01:15.960
read, we're bringing it to God in prayer.

00:01:13.979 --> 00:01:17.939
So, I just wanted to say thank you and we

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:19.798
appreciate you so much for blessing

00:01:17.939 --> 00:01:21.658
our family and for all the likes and

00:01:19.799 --> 00:01:23.220
the subscribers.

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:25.920
We love you."We

00:01:23.220 --> 00:01:29.700
just want to say thank you,

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:32.880
definitely. I was praying about the

00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:34.920
border and all the things going on there: the sex

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:38.039
trafficking, the

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:39.780
drugs, and all the evil that's going on

00:01:38.040 --> 00:01:41.820
down there. The Lord said to me,

00:01:39.780 --> 00:01:43.439
"Brandon, I'm going to tell you something.

00:01:43.439 --> 00:01:49.380
What the devil meant for bad through the

00:01:46.619 --> 00:01:51.840
Democratic Party and all that they do

00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:53.699
by having these open borders—the hundreds of thousands of

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:55.740
people flooding

00:01:53.700 --> 00:01:58.200
over—you

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:00.600
don't need to worry about

00:01:59.700 --> 00:02:04.200
that,

00:02:00.600 --> 00:02:07.798
for I have a plan."I was like,

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:10.619
"Oh, wow."He said, "Brandon,

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:13.260
what the devil meant for bad, I'm going to

00:02:10.619 --> 00:02:16.080
turn it around for good. These

00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:17.640
people are searching for the

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:19.739
American Dream.

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:21.660
There's a lot of evil coming across the

00:02:19.739 --> 00:02:24.540
border also, not just innocent people

00:02:21.660 --> 00:02:26.280
that are wanting a new life. There

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:27.840
are

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:30.000
terrorist elements and bad

00:02:27.840 --> 00:02:33.120
stuff happening, but Brandon,

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:35.700
there's a great revival that's about to

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:37.800
hit this nation and the world.

00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:39.599
It's coming.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:41.400
These people that are coming are going to

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:44.099
get caught up in this great

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:45.959
outpouring of my Spirit on this nation,

00:02:44.099 --> 00:02:49.140
and there's going to be a great harvest of souls at the Southern Border."He said there's going to be a great move of

00:02:45.959 --> 00:02:50.879
God on

00:02:49.140 --> 00:02:53.160
the Southern Border,

00:02:50.879 --> 00:02:55.079
with

00:02:55.080 --> 00:03:00.360
healings and restoration in people's

00:02:58.019 --> 00:03:02.940
lives. He said, "Just get ready.

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:06.540
Don't worry about it.

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:08.819
My Son's return is right at the door.

00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:11.519
You're thinking

00:03:08.819 --> 00:03:14.940
too small. Do you realize what's about to

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:17.340
happen? A powerful move of my

00:03:14.940 --> 00:03:19.260
Spirit is about to hit this Earth.

00:03:17.340 --> 00:03:20.760
Don't worry about all that fleshly

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:22.859
stuff; there's going to be a great

00:03:20.760 --> 00:03:25.379
outpouring of my Spirit upon this Earth

00:03:22.860 --> 00:03:27.659
like never before."He said, "Brandon,

00:03:25.379 --> 00:03:29.579
don't worry about all that stuff.

00:03:27.659 --> 00:03:31.859
I'm going to turn it

00:03:29.580 --> 00:03:34.379
around for good in my

00:03:31.860 --> 00:03:36.780
favor.

00:03:36.780 --> 00:03:40.319
Watch what I'm about to do on

00:03:38.640 --> 00:03:43.379
the Southern Border."A great revival

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:46.859
is about to break forth.

00:03:43.379 --> 00:03:48.899
He said, "Remember this: if

00:03:46.860 --> 00:03:51.480
the devil would have known what was

00:03:48.900 --> 00:03:53.099
going to happen with Jesus, they

00:03:51.480 --> 00:03:55.920
wouldn't have crucified Him. Remember

00:03:53.099 --> 00:03:57.720
this: if the devil would have

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:00.119
known what was going to happen on the

00:03:57.720 --> 00:04:02.640
Southern Border with the revival

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:04.739
that's about to break forth, he said he wouldn't have

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:07.079
done this either. I'm going to turn it around, son. Watch."Whenever he said that, I felt the power of God all over me. He said, "I'm

00:04:04.739 --> 00:04:09.120
going to turn it around.

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:17.280
There's going to be all this drug

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:20.399
trafficking, all this drug trafficking.

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:22.859
Watch what happens."God's coming on the

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:24.900
scene. He's going to show up and

00:04:22.860 --> 00:04:26.400
embarrass the devil again.

00:04:24.900 --> 00:04:28.859
They're not going to be able to cover it up—CNN,

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:30.060
Fox, all these people—they're

00:04:28.860 --> 00:04:32.280
going to see it and ask,

00:04:30.060 --> 00:04:34.620
"What is going on

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:37.440
down there?"because a

00:04:34.620 --> 00:04:39.180
great move of God is about to pour out

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:41.219
even on the Southern Border, all

00:04:39.180 --> 00:04:44.520
throughout Texas, Mexico,

00:04:41.220 --> 00:04:47.100
Arizona, and

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:49.799
California. Get ready!

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:51.180
A great revival is coming, and

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:53.280
it's going to start on the

00:04:51.180 --> 00:04:55.740
Southern Border, too.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:58.138
There's not a devil in hell that can

00:04:55.740 --> 00:04:59.639
stop what God's about to do.

00:04:58.139 --> 00:05:02.160
It's going to

00:04:59.639 --> 00:05:03.840
be like popcorn, and

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:05.880
Jesus is going to do it.

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:07.380
I just

00:05:05.880 --> 00:05:09.600
want to encourage you because I know a

00:05:07.380 --> 00:05:11.940
lot of people have been in fear of

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:14.220
Al-Qaeda and whoever else is coming

00:05:11.940 --> 00:05:16.380
across. We hear all this stuff

00:05:14.220 --> 00:05:18.419
on the news about what's going on

00:05:16.380 --> 00:05:20.400
with these children, but God's

00:05:18.419 --> 00:05:23.099
fixing to put an end to all that.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:25.739
He's going to move in a great, mighty way

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:28.020
in these last days. So, get excited

00:05:25.740 --> 00:05:30.600
about what God is getting ready to do. Pray and

00:05:28.020 --> 00:05:31.919
send laborers across their path.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:34.320
It's going to be one of

00:05:31.919 --> 00:05:36.240
the glory spots. I know

00:05:34.320 --> 00:05:38.400
that God is fixing—He said He's up to

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:40.860
something

00:05:38.400 --> 00:05:43.620
big. Get ready for something big, family.

00:05:40.860 --> 00:05:46.560
A lot of people ask me

00:05:43.620 --> 00:05:49.440
about prayer tips.

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:52.020
The Bible says, "If ye

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:54.479
abide in me and my words abide in you, ye

00:05:52.020 --> 00:05:55.979
shall ask what you will and it shall

00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:58.020
be done."You need to get that

00:05:55.979 --> 00:06:00.180
scripture down inside

00:05:58.020 --> 00:06:02.159
you.

00:06:02.160 --> 00:06:07.680
The Word needs to back your

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:09.840
prayer to get the

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:12.360
manifestation

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:15.299
you're looking for. A

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:17.280
lot of people start praying with

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:19.620
doubt and unbelief, but

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:20.520
the Word backing your prayer moves your

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:23.400
mountain and takes

00:06:20.520 --> 00:06:26.880
things

00:06:23.400 --> 00:06:29.219
out of the way.

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:31.620
And if you're men, if you're not

00:06:29.220 --> 00:06:34.380
honoring your wives, it talks about

00:06:31.620 --> 00:06:36.180
your prayers being hindered.

00:06:34.380 --> 00:06:38.940
I'm going to put that scripture here in

00:06:36.180 --> 00:06:41.699
the description. So you need to get

00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:43.560
strife out of your home

00:06:41.699 --> 00:06:45.720
and

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:47.340
get that Word down inside

00:06:45.720 --> 00:06:50.160
your heart so you pray the scriptures.

00:06:47.340 --> 00:06:52.679
Then, you need to take the "care"out

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:55.080
of your prayer. You've got to take

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:58.380
the care out of your prayer because it

00:06:55.080 --> 00:07:00.659
hinders things. "Be

00:06:58.380 --> 00:07:02.639
careful for nothing."You don't need to

00:07:00.660 --> 00:07:06.000
take the care on it. For

00:07:02.639 --> 00:07:08.160
example, I was praying

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:10.020
over my daughter, Megan, taking on the care

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:12.539
of all the stuff

00:07:12.539 --> 00:07:17.400
she's going through.

00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:22.138
Fear was

00:07:19.979 --> 00:07:23.400
trying to hit me about the future. the

00:07:22.139 --> 00:07:24.900
devil

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:26.039
always tries to come and speak:

00:07:24.900 --> 00:07:27.179
"What are you going to do now? What

00:07:26.039 --> 00:07:28.620
are you going to

00:07:27.180 --> 00:07:30.180
do about your little girl when she gets

00:07:28.620 --> 00:07:32.520
older? What happens when

00:07:30.180 --> 00:07:34.259
you go home to be with the

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:36.419
Lord? She's going to be left here by

00:07:34.259 --> 00:07:38.759
herself."All

00:07:36.419 --> 00:07:41.340
this doubt and unbelief was

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:45.240
continually nagging at me:

00:07:41.340 --> 00:07:48.000
fear, fear, fear. Fear tolerated is faith

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:49.979
contaminated. You've got to

00:07:49.979 --> 00:07:54.419
cast down fear

00:07:51.900 --> 00:07:57.780
because it will rob you of your faith.

00:07:54.419 --> 00:07:59.940
Perfect love casteth out all fear. If

00:07:57.780 --> 00:08:02.758
you're walking in fear and in torment,

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:05.039
fear has torment, and he that feareth is

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:06.120
not made perfect in love.

00:08:08.940 --> 00:08:13.319
You can't allow him to build a

00:08:11.220 --> 00:08:15.479
stronghold in your thought life.

00:08:13.319 --> 00:08:18.240
Cast those thoughts down.

00:08:15.479 --> 00:08:20.758
Get the Word of God and say, "Devil, I

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:23.099
doubt your doubt!

00:08:20.759 --> 00:08:25.319
You're not going to

00:08:23.099 --> 00:08:27.659
speak your unbelief into

00:08:25.319 --> 00:08:29.039
my head. Take that

00:08:27.660 --> 00:08:31.020
back to hell where you came from.

00:08:31.020 --> 00:08:36.419
I'm walking in love.""Father, I thank you that you love me enough. You

00:08:33.659 --> 00:08:38.039
love

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:43.620
Megan

00:08:40.979 --> 00:08:45.959
and you have a

00:08:43.620 --> 00:08:48.779
plan for her life. I thank you that your

00:08:45.959 --> 00:08:51.479
Word says that by the stripes of Jesus, Megan is

00:08:48.779 --> 00:08:53.160
healed. You have a perfect plan

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:56.339
for my baby,

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:58.800
and I'm not going to worry about her future anymore."If you

00:08:56.339 --> 00:09:01.320
take it

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:03.180
on,

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:05.160
you may be laying in bed dying of

00:09:03.180 --> 00:09:08.099
an

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:10.980
incurable disease, and

00:09:08.100 --> 00:09:13.019
the care and fear try to rise up on

00:09:10.980 --> 00:09:15.240
the inside of you, trying to rob you of

00:09:13.019 --> 00:09:17.459
your faith. You've got to speak to those

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:19.800
circumstances and realize

00:09:17.459 --> 00:09:22.079
that even in the last seconds,

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:27.360
God can still turn it.

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:33.120
All things are

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:35.399
possible to him who believes.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:37.860
Faith will move your mountain. I'm

00:09:35.399 --> 00:09:40.820
telling you, just believe and

00:09:37.860 --> 00:09:44.580
stand.

00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:46.380
Never give up. Even when

00:09:44.580 --> 00:09:48.120
I deal with it, he tries

00:09:46.380 --> 00:09:49.920
to drive me: "What are you

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:51.480
going to do now?

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:53.640
You don't have

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:55.980
any money saved back for her for going in a

00:09:53.640 --> 00:09:57.959
home that's going to cost

00:09:55.980 --> 00:10:00.480
you hundreds of thousands of dollars

00:09:57.959 --> 00:10:03.959
a year."I say,

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:05.940
"It's not my problem, devil. My God's got

00:10:03.959 --> 00:10:08.399
this. He's big, and He's going to turn it

00:10:05.940 --> 00:10:10.440
around for me."And you know what? I was

00:10:08.399 --> 00:10:13.200
praying, like I said, I was just interceding

00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:15.959
and the Lord spoke to me. He said, 'Brandon,

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:18.779
do you know what? There will be a

00:10:15.959 --> 00:10:20.160
generation, son, that doesn't ever taste

00:10:18.779 --> 00:10:22.620
death,

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:25.140
and you're that generation.

00:10:22.620 --> 00:10:27.839
You're never going to see or taste death.'He

00:10:25.140 --> 00:10:30.959
said, 'My son is coming.

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:33.720
My son is coming. I've got this. Cast your

00:10:30.959 --> 00:10:36.839
care, Brandon. Cast it. Cast your care.

00:10:33.720 --> 00:10:39.899
Don't take the care anymore.

00:10:36.839 --> 00:10:41.519
Take the care out of your prayer.

00:10:39.899 --> 00:10:43.500
I've got you.'And

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:46.740
when he said that,

00:10:43.500 --> 00:10:47.940
peace flooded my heart and I said, 'Lord, I

00:10:46.740 --> 00:10:49.800
trust you.'Trust

00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:51.600
in the Lord with all your heart

00:10:49.800 --> 00:10:54.300
and lean not unto thy own understanding,

00:10:51.600 --> 00:10:56.160
but in all thy ways acknowledge Him and

00:10:54.300 --> 00:10:58.920
He shall direct your path.

00:10:56.160 --> 00:11:01.199
Trust in Him. He's got you. He loves you.

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:02.819
He's never going to let

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:04.440
you down. He's going to carry you through

00:11:02.820 --> 00:11:06.180
your trials. He's going to carry you

00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:10.320
through the tribulations, just like he's

00:11:06.180 --> 00:11:13.319
done for me. I am just human, y'all.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:15.360
Everybody was asking for prayer,

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:18.180
and everybody's asking me for

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:21.180
healing and for all this stuff. I

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:23.760
don't control the switch; Jesus does. But

00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:25.680
the same Jesus that lives in me

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:28.079
lives in you.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:30.420
You have the same power and authority

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:32.880
living on the inside of you that

00:11:30.420 --> 00:11:34.500
lives in me. Greater is He that is in me

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:36.120
than he that is in the world. Greater is He

00:11:34.500 --> 00:11:36.899
that is in you than he that is in the

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:40.680
world.

00:11:36.899 --> 00:11:43.380
Jesus lives on the inside of you.

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:45.779
It doesn't take me to pray for you; you can

00:11:43.380 --> 00:11:47.640
pray for yourself. You have that

00:11:45.779 --> 00:11:50.519
authority that dwells on the inside of

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:52.319
you. You can speak to your mountain and

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:54.120
it will hear you, and it will depart and be

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:57.000
cast into the sea. It will depart

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:59.160
from you and be cast into the sea. You

00:11:57.000 --> 00:12:00.440
have mountain-moving faith on the inside

00:11:59.160 --> 00:12:04.079
of you.

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:06.420
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by

00:12:04.079 --> 00:12:08.519
the word of God. That's the same way I

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:10.860
got it. I don't have

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:13.019
Superman faith. I have faith that has

00:12:10.860 --> 00:12:16.079
been consistent. It's like going to the

00:12:13.019 --> 00:12:17.640
gym. You go and you lift

00:12:16.079 --> 00:12:20.099
the weights.

00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:22.380
You're working out, and you may see small

00:12:20.100 --> 00:12:24.959
results. You may see a little bit

00:12:22.380 --> 00:12:27.720
here and there, but I've seen people

00:12:24.959 --> 00:12:30.239
that are huge bodybuilders and you know

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:32.700
how they got there? Not by one time going

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:36.320
to the gym, not by two times going to the

00:12:32.700 --> 00:12:39.440
gym, but consistency

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:42.360
is what brings the results.

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:44.519
When you are consistent with the word of

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:46.700
God, when you get the word of God inside

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:49.860
of you and it's consistency

00:12:46.700 --> 00:12:52.380
every day—every day you're hitting it—you

00:12:49.860 --> 00:12:54.600
know those divots in

00:12:52.380 --> 00:12:57.420
the caves, or the little water dripping

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:59.040
on the rock, and all of a

00:12:57.420 --> 00:13:01.800
sudden over the course of time it

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:04.260
creates a crater inside of it. That's

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:06.240
what happens when you keep

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:09.060
the word inside of you. Like a little

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:11.220
drip, you keep it in there. If your flesh

00:13:09.060 --> 00:13:14.459
wants to eat three times a day—breakfast,

00:13:11.220 --> 00:13:17.220
lunch, and dinner—you should feed your

00:13:14.459 --> 00:13:19.979
spirit some kind of food at least twice

00:13:17.220 --> 00:13:23.100
a day. Get something on the inside of you.

00:13:19.980 --> 00:13:24.839
How desperate are you for change in your

00:13:23.100 --> 00:13:27.300
life?

00:13:24.839 --> 00:13:29.220
People say, 'Oh, I need change in my life.

00:13:27.300 --> 00:13:31.560
I'm spiritually drained. I'm spiritually

00:13:29.220 --> 00:13:33.300
going through all this

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:36.540
stuff.'How

00:13:33.300 --> 00:13:38.939
desperate are you for that change? You've

00:13:36.540 --> 00:13:41.699
got to be desperate. You've got to be

00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:45.300
like a bulldog on a bone. You've got to say,

00:13:41.700 --> 00:13:48.360
'I'm not going to give up until I get my

00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:51.060
miracle. I'm not giving up until I get a

00:13:48.360 --> 00:13:53.279
touch from the Lord.

00:13:51.060 --> 00:13:55.199
I want to hear you, Father.'I'm

00:13:53.279 --> 00:13:57.779
telling you, I'm not

00:13:55.200 --> 00:14:00.120
anything special; I've just been diligent.

00:13:57.779 --> 00:14:01.620
I just go and I get in the word.

00:14:03.720 --> 00:14:09.380
I've been desperate. When a man

00:14:06.779 --> 00:14:12.000
can hardly read or write or do anything

00:14:09.380 --> 00:14:14.160
and you see other men

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:15.959
that are able to

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:18.000
provide for their families and take care

00:14:15.959 --> 00:14:20.459
of their families, it's very

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:22.920
humbling to me

00:14:20.459 --> 00:14:25.560
because I want to be that. And so I've

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:27.240
had to press in even harder because of

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:29.219
the learning problems that I've dealt

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:31.200
with. I'm getting in the word, saying, 'God,

00:14:29.220 --> 00:14:34.620
show me how to take care of my family.

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:36.480
Show me what to do.'I

00:14:34.620 --> 00:14:37.860
know that you're the provider. I know

00:14:36.480 --> 00:14:39.300
you're the one that provides all my

00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:41.459
needs according to your riches in glory.

00:14:39.300 --> 00:14:44.579
But Father, I thank you that you

00:14:41.459 --> 00:14:47.638
said you blessed my hands

00:14:44.579 --> 00:14:50.579
and anything I put my hands to, I will

00:14:47.639 --> 00:14:52.500
prosper. So I get in those words, I find

00:14:50.579 --> 00:14:54.899
things, I ask Him, 'Father, show me what to

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:58.380
invest in. Show me what to do.'I look for

00:14:54.899 --> 00:15:01.199
Him every day, all day long. 'God, what do

00:14:58.380 --> 00:15:03.839
you have for me today?'Wake up every day anticipating,

00:15:01.199 --> 00:15:06.899
'What's on your agenda

00:15:03.839 --> 00:15:08.459
for my life? Not my agenda, but what's on

00:15:06.899 --> 00:15:10.199
your agenda? What do you want me to do

00:15:08.459 --> 00:15:12.779
today, Lord?'A lot of you might have

00:15:10.199 --> 00:15:14.880
to go to work from eight to five,

00:15:12.779 --> 00:15:17.160
but you can still seek Him for

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:19.920
what's going on in

00:15:17.160 --> 00:15:22.199
your life. 'Lord, I thank you. I

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:24.779
submit myself unto you. I just listen to

00:15:22.199 --> 00:15:27.479
you, God. I thank you. I'm desperate. I'm

00:15:24.779 --> 00:15:29.579
hungry, Father. Speak to me. Show me the

00:15:27.480 --> 00:15:32.040
hidden things.'Father, I pray

00:15:29.579 --> 00:15:35.099
Ephesians 1:18 over my mind: 'let the eyes

00:15:32.040 --> 00:15:36.839
of my understanding be enlightened, let

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:38.940
me know the hope of my calling.'Show me, God, show me what

00:15:36.839 --> 00:15:41.760
you have for me

00:15:38.940 --> 00:15:44.880
today. When you get desperate for

00:15:41.760 --> 00:15:47.279
God, it says those that seek Me

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:49.199
will find Me. But He wants to see how

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:51.420
hungry you are. He wants to see how

00:15:49.199 --> 00:15:53.639
desperate you are, because whenever you

00:15:51.420 --> 00:15:56.219
get desperate and you get hungry and you

00:15:53.639 --> 00:15:58.680
start seeking Him, God shows up. But I'm

00:15:56.220 --> 00:16:00.959
going to tell you this: I go to Him a lot

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:02.880
of times with singing. Last time when

00:16:00.959 --> 00:16:04.018
I sang those songs in the

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:05.820
last video, that was the first time for

00:16:04.019 --> 00:16:07.740
me to ever sing in public

00:16:05.820 --> 00:16:09.060
to anybody other than my wife and my

00:16:07.740 --> 00:16:11.779
children.

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:15.540
I sing all the time.

00:16:11.779 --> 00:16:17.699
Praise brings the presence down. Praise

00:16:15.540 --> 00:16:20.399
does. That's a key of

00:16:17.699 --> 00:16:22.620
spiritual warfare: worship. When you

00:16:20.399 --> 00:16:25.139
get in there with thanksgiving... I enter

00:16:22.620 --> 00:16:25.860
into His courts with thanksgiving in my

00:16:25.139 --> 00:16:28.079
heart;

00:16:25.860 --> 00:16:30.180
I enter His courts with praise. I thank

00:16:28.079 --> 00:16:31.979
Him. I thank Him for the electric. Thank

00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:34.859
Him for your water. Thank Him for the

00:16:31.980 --> 00:16:37.320
food you ate. Take time to thank Him and

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:39.240
worship Him for everything you have. I

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:40.800
sit there, and in my prayer time, even

00:16:39.240 --> 00:16:43.620
when my son and my wife were all praying,

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:45.899
I just take a moment. It may be ten percent

00:16:43.620 --> 00:16:47.639
of the prayer: 'God, I just want to

00:16:45.899 --> 00:16:49.740
tell you thank you for what you provided

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:52.860
for me today. Thank you for the clothes

00:16:49.740 --> 00:16:55.019
on my back. Thank you for the shoes on

00:16:52.860 --> 00:16:57.180
my feet. Thank you, Father, that I have air

00:16:55.019 --> 00:16:59.279
in my lungs. Thank you, Lord, that we're

00:16:57.180 --> 00:17:01.380
healed. Thank you, Lord, my children are whole.

00:16:59.279 --> 00:17:04.020
Thank you, Lord, for the blessing

00:17:01.380 --> 00:17:06.419
of the trees. Thank you, Lord, for my

00:17:04.020 --> 00:17:10.020
grass out front. Thank you, Lord, for

00:17:06.419 --> 00:17:13.020
the flowers, for the birds, for

00:17:10.020 --> 00:17:15.059
my dogs, for my chickens,

00:17:13.020 --> 00:17:18.179
for everything you've given me.

00:17:15.059 --> 00:17:21.020
God, you've

00:17:18.179 --> 00:17:23.339
been so good to

00:17:21.020 --> 00:17:26.160
me.'You've

00:17:23.339 --> 00:17:28.260
got to get praise down

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:30.179
inside of your heart. If you want a

00:17:28.260 --> 00:17:32.280
manifestation of the glory of God in

00:17:30.179 --> 00:17:34.440
your house, you've got to be grateful for

00:17:32.280 --> 00:17:37.980
what He's done for you,

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:40.440
because He's no respecter of persons. And

00:17:37.980 --> 00:17:42.900
if He's going to be good to me, He'll be

00:17:40.440 --> 00:17:44.520
good to you. I'm telling you, God isn't going to

00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:45.960
look at me in any other special

00:17:44.520 --> 00:17:49.020
way than you.

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:51.720
I just take time to worship Him. A lot of

00:17:49.020 --> 00:17:54.240
people are lazy. They don't want to go

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:56.280
out to the spiritual gym.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:58.679
I think it

00:17:56.280 --> 00:18:01.799
sucks to run on a treadmill, but

00:17:58.679 --> 00:18:04.440
some people enjoy it. I don't. But I

00:18:01.799 --> 00:18:06.840
enjoy going to the spiritual gym.

00:18:04.440 --> 00:18:09.419
I like to see the things in the

00:18:06.840 --> 00:18:10.799
spirit. I like to see angels. I like to

00:18:09.419 --> 00:18:13.620
see those things. But I'm going to tell

00:18:10.799 --> 00:18:16.260
you all, I never pursued one time for an

00:18:13.620 --> 00:18:18.659
angel encounter. I never pursued one time

00:18:16.260 --> 00:18:21.120
for a Jesus encounter that I've had, or

00:18:18.660 --> 00:18:22.320
any kind of manifestation. I just seek

00:18:21.120 --> 00:18:25.918
His face. If you

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:28.500
seek His face, you

00:18:25.919 --> 00:18:30.059
can have it. If you seek Him, you can have

00:18:28.500 --> 00:18:32.280
what's in His hand.

00:18:30.059 --> 00:18:35.639
If you seek what's in His hand—His

00:18:32.280 --> 00:18:37.020
provision—you

00:18:35.640 --> 00:18:39.000
don't want to do that. You want to seek Him.

00:18:37.020 --> 00:18:41.280
You want to seek His face.

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:43.200
He's not looking for a handout God.

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:44.520
'I thank you that you give me

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:46.980
this stuff,'and you're always coming to

00:18:44.520 --> 00:18:50.760
Him whining. He knows what you have need

00:18:46.980 --> 00:18:54.360
of. He knows you're hurting. If

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:56.340
you have something going on in your life,

00:18:54.360 --> 00:18:59.340
come to Him in worship.

00:18:56.340 --> 00:19:01.860
Come to just sing Him a song. 'Lord, I just

00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:04.080
want to sing you a song.'And I just start

00:19:01.860 --> 00:19:07.260
singing Him a song. 'You are beautiful

00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:09.899
beyond description.'You

00:19:07.260 --> 00:19:15.660
just start singing to Him.

00:19:09.900 --> 00:19:17.460
'Father, I stand, I stand in awe of you.'Just

00:19:15.660 --> 00:19:22.679
start singing to Him.

00:19:17.460 --> 00:19:25.580
'I stand, I stand in awe of you,

00:19:22.679 --> 00:19:29.400
holy God to whom all

00:19:25.580 --> 00:19:35.280
praise is due.

00:19:29.400 --> 00:19:38.340
I stand in awe of you.'Worship

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:40.200
Him. Worship Him. I start

00:19:38.340 --> 00:19:43.379
feeling His presence; He starts filling

00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:46.980
the house. 'Oh Lord, you're beautiful. Oh,

00:19:43.380 --> 00:19:50.760
you're worthy. Oh, you're worthy, Lord.

00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:53.039
You're worthy to be

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:56.100
praised.'God,

00:19:53.039 --> 00:19:58.860
thank you, Jesus. And the more you do that,

00:19:56.100 --> 00:20:00.299
the more you practice His presence, the

00:19:58.860 --> 00:20:01.979
more He starts to come

00:20:00.299 --> 00:20:05.100
and the more He feels comfortable being

00:20:01.980 --> 00:20:08.039
around you. The Holy Spirit's a gentleman.

00:20:05.100 --> 00:20:10.379
He is not going to force Himself on you.

00:20:08.039 --> 00:20:12.240
He goes where He's invited.

00:20:10.380 --> 00:20:15.380
People, you need to understand:

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:19.200
He loves each and every single one of us.

00:20:15.380 --> 00:20:22.260
He loves us and He wants to come and be

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:24.000
in your house, but a lot of times the

00:20:22.260 --> 00:20:26.100
atmosphere is not conducive for Him

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:28.020
because you've got all kinds of trash

00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:30.600
going on in your home.

00:20:28.020 --> 00:20:32.220
I'm telling you: make the atmosphere

00:20:30.600 --> 00:20:35.159
perfect,

00:20:32.220 --> 00:20:38.780
make the house perfect

00:20:35.160 --> 00:20:42.240
in the spirit realm by worship. He loves

00:20:38.780 --> 00:20:43.740
worship. Worship Him, and I'm telling you

00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:46.080
He'll come in your house and abide with

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:47.220
you. And He's great; He'll come. You'll be in

00:20:46.080 --> 00:20:51.020
there, and all of a sudden you start

00:20:47.220 --> 00:20:52.620
worshiping the Lord. Hallelujah!

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:55.200
Hallelujah!

00:20:52.620 --> 00:20:57.120
Oh Lord, I praise You!

00:20:55.200 --> 00:21:00.059
They don't have to be anything serious;

00:20:57.120 --> 00:21:03.239
just sing to Him: 'Oh God, You're so good

00:21:00.059 --> 00:21:05.700
to me, thank You for all You've done.'And

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:07.740
you start worshiping Him,

00:21:05.700 --> 00:21:10.559
and I'm telling you—I've said it before—when

00:21:07.740 --> 00:21:13.140
you get real, God has to get real

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:15.418
with you. And so, you know, I really

00:21:13.140 --> 00:21:18.840
thought that these prayer tips

00:21:15.419 --> 00:21:22.200
might help you. This is a walk; this is a

00:21:18.840 --> 00:21:25.340
way of life for me. This is how I live my

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:29.100
life. I stay in an attitude of gratitude.

00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:31.500
I take the care out of my prayer. I try

00:21:29.100 --> 00:21:34.439
so hard to not let the devil come in

00:21:31.500 --> 00:21:37.679
with thoughts of fear. I feed on the word.

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:40.559
Get in the word—priority number one

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:43.140
above all of it. Get in the word. If you

00:21:40.559 --> 00:21:45.120
abide in Me and My words abide in you,

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:48.419
you shall ask what you will and it shall

00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:50.459
be done. Remember that; get that down on

00:21:48.419 --> 00:21:52.980
the inside of you. You've got to get that

00:21:50.460 --> 00:21:55.860
down, and it has to be a

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:58.320
foundation of a rock—a rock-solid

00:21:55.860 --> 00:22:00.299
foundation of the word inside of you.

00:21:58.320 --> 00:22:02.340
Build your house on that so that

00:22:00.299 --> 00:22:04.860
when the winds and the waves and

00:22:02.340 --> 00:22:07.439
the storms come, it's not able to knock

00:22:04.860 --> 00:22:10.500
your house down. Remember that the devil

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:12.299
always comes to kill, steal, and destroy,

00:22:10.500 --> 00:22:14.820
but you've just got to get the word down

00:22:12.299 --> 00:22:16.918
inside of you. And He that dwells in the

00:22:14.820 --> 00:22:19.980
secret place of the Most High shall

00:22:16.919 --> 00:22:21.659
abide in the shadow of the Almighty. Stay

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:23.940
in that secret place;

00:22:21.659 --> 00:22:25.919
stay in that secret place of the shadow

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:28.740
of the Almighty today. I love you guys.

00:22:25.919 --> 00:22:30.360
Put a smile on your face and a song in

00:22:28.740 --> 00:22:32.820
your heart, and I just thank you for

00:22:30.360 --> 00:22:35.340
being with my family here. If you all

00:22:32.820 --> 00:22:38.399
could please like and share this video,

00:22:35.340 --> 00:22:40.500
it really helps me to get the word out,

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:43.020
to get the gospel out. I just want to

00:22:40.500 --> 00:22:44.280
tell you: Jesus loves you today. He loves

00:22:43.020 --> 00:22:46.620
you so much;

00:22:44.280 --> 00:22:48.480
I hope you realize that.

00:22:46.620 --> 00:22:52.219
Thank you for being a part of my family. God

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:52.220
bless you and have a good day.

